Fixes: a22712a96291 ("mlxsw: core: Fix devlink unregister flow")
Signed-off-by: Ido Schimmel <idosch@nvidia.com>
Reported-by: Vadim Pasternak <vadimp@nvidia.com>
Tested-by: Oleksandr Shamray <oleksandrs@nvidia.com>
